- The shell is very powerful because it also allows automation through scripts.

User Space

- This is where all applications run, like browsers, editors, and software tools.
- Programs in this layer cannot directly affect the kernel, which helps keep the system safe.
- If an application crashes, it usually stays within this layer and does not bring down the whole
  system.

